# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This repository publishes ONLY the public /web site. Everything else in the
# project — the arena tooling, provisioning, and raw per-round record — is
# operational and contains live credentials, flag secrets, real infrastructure,
# and unredacted agent transcripts. It stays private. Ignore everything, then
# allow only the vetted site.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/CHANGELOG.md
!/web/

# Operational tooling — CODE ONLY, sanitized of infra addresses + seeded secrets
# (those live in the gitignored arena.local.json; see arena.local.example.json).
# Deliberately NOT tracked: ansible/ (flag secrets + inventory IPs), terraform
# state, the raw rounds/ record, arena-firewall.md, and the built HTML artifacts
# under site/ — each needs its own review before it could go public.
!/arena_config.py
!/arena.local.example.json
!/gate.py
!/orchestrate.py
!/pull_transcripts.py
!/race_clock.py
!/referee.py
!/spec.py
!/verify.py
!/watch_round.py
!/site/
/site/*
!/site/build_replay.py
!/site/live_feed.py
!/site/live_redact.py

# Secrets / caches that must never ship, even from inside an allowed path:
**/arena.local.json
**/.recall/
**/.impeccable/
**/.DS_Store
**/.env
**/.dev.vars
**/.admin-token
**/*.feed-token
**/*.pve-token
**/.wrangler/
